title: Oldenburg Landtag Elections
new-page: true
tags: event
priority: 1
view-if: (year = oldenburg_election_year and month >= oldenburg_election_month) or (year > oldenburg_election_year)
on-departure: oldenburg_election_year = oldenburg_election_year + 4 if oldenburg_snap_election_called == 0; oldenburg_election_year = year + 4 if oldenburg_snap_election_called == 1; oldenburg_election_month = month if oldenburg_snap_election_called == 1; oldenburg_snap_election_called = 0
set-jump: oldenburg_landtag_results

= Oldenburg Landtag Elections, [+ month : month +] [+ year +]

Oldenburg holds Landtag elections. This system reuses federal party support, applies Oldenburg weights and the DNVP/CNBL split rules, normalizes results, and allocates **48** seats with D'Hondt.

- @calculate_oldenburg_landtag: Count the votes.

@calculate_oldenburg_landtag
on-arrival: oldenburg_government = 3 if oldenburg_government == undefined; oldenburg_leader = "Theodor Tantzen" if oldenburg_leader == undefined; oldenburg_majority_cabinet = 0 if oldenburg_majority_cabinet == undefined
go-to: election_algorithm
set-jump: oldenburg_landtag_results

@oldenburg_landtag_results
on-arrival: {! Q.oldenburg_next_election_year_preview = Number(Q.oldenburg_election_year) || Number(Q.year) || 0; Q.oldenburg_next_election_month_preview = Q.oldenburg_election_month; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.calculateOldenburgLandtagResults === 'function') { window.calculateOldenburgLandtagResults(Q); } !}

= Oldenburg Landtag election results

Next Oldenburg election after this Landtag is due in **[+ oldenburg_next_election_month_preview : month +] [+ oldenburg_next_election_year_preview +]**.

Oldenburg Landtag seats: **[+ oldenburg_landtag_total_seats +] / 48**.

Current Oldenburg government: **[+ oldenburg_current_government_name +]** ([+ oldenburg_current_government_parties +]) led by **[+ oldenburg_leader +]**.

Current government seats: **[+ oldenburg_current_government_seats +] / 48**. Status: **[+ oldenburg_current_government_status +]**. Majority cabinet: **[+ oldenburg_majority_cabinet +]**.

Current government leverage: **[+ oldenburg_leverage +]**.

