= Choose an Oldenburg coalition

A coalition is selectable if it controls at least **25** of the **48** Landtag seats. Before 1930, a technocratic cabinet may also be selected. If no listed coalition has a majority, the incumbent Oldenburg government may continue as a minority cabinet.

- @oldenburg_select_technocratic
- @oldenburg_select_spd_z_ddp
- @oldenburg_select_z_ddp_dvp
- @oldenburg_select_ddp_dvp_wp
- @oldenburg_select_ddp_dnvp_z_dvp
- @oldenburg_select_dnvp_z_dvp_cnbl
- @oldenburg_select_nsdap_dnvp
- @oldenburg_select_nsdap_majority
- @new_oldenburg_elections: Call new Oldenburg Landtag elections.
- @root: Continue without changing the Oldenburg government.

@oldenburg_select_technocratic
title: Technocratic cabinet
subtitle: None — [+ oldenburg_technocratic_coalition_seats +] / 48 — [+ oldenburg_technocratic_coalition_status +]
view-if: oldenburg_technocratic_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.oldenburg_government = 1; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateOldenburgCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateOldenburgCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: oldenburg_leader_selection

